{
  "video_id": "5w5BhwLzoqg",
  "title": "For the love of birds | Washington Wachira",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 12760.0,
      "end_time": 14416.0,
      "text": "With me here today"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 14440.0,
      "end_time": 16160.0,
      "text": "I brought something beautiful."
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 16920.0,
      "end_time": 21576.0,
      "text": "This is a feather from one of the most beautiful birds we have in Kenya,"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 21600.0,
      "end_time": 23560.0,
      "text": "the crested guinea fowl."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 24600.0,
      "end_time": 27536.0,
      "text": "But this feather is more than just that."
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 27560.0,
      "end_time": 29816.0,
      "text": "If you&#39;ve taken time when you are outdoors"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 29840.0,
      "end_time": 31736.0,
      "text": "to look at the feathers around you,"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 31760.0,
      "end_time": 32976.0,
      "text": "you&#39;ll have noticed"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 33000.0,
      "end_time": 36736.0,
      "text": "that there is this huge variety of different sizes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 36760.0,
      "end_time": 38960.0,
      "text": "shapes and even colors."
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 39840.0,
      "end_time": 44536.0,
      "text": "The feather is one of the most astonishing pieces of technology"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 44560.0,
      "end_time": 47960.0,
      "text": "invented by the natural world,"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 47120.0,
      "end_time": 52135.0,
      "text": "and for centuries, this feather has helped birds to keep dry,"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 52160.0,
      "end_time": 55400.0,
      "text": "to keep warm and even power flight."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 56280.0,
      "end_time": 60360.0,
      "text": "Only one section of the tree of life can actually make a feather."
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 61400.0,
      "end_time": 63336.0,
      "text": "Among all the world&#39;s animals,"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 63360.0,
      "end_time": 65536.0,
      "text": "birds are the only ones who can make something"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 65560.0,
      "end_time": 66894.0,
      "text": "like what I&#39;m holding today."
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 67960.0,
      "end_time": 70336.0,
      "text": "I personally have given them a nickname,"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 70360.0,
      "end_time": 72800.0,
      "text": "and I like to call them the feathermakers."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 74360.0,
      "end_time": 79816.0,
      "text": "It is the major difference between birds and any other animals we have on earth,"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 79840.0,
      "end_time": 83456.0,
      "text": "and if you can&#39;t make a feather, you cannot call yourself a bird."
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 83480.0,
      "end_time": 85696.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 85720.0,
      "end_time": 88816.0,
      "text": "For us humans, who are earthbound,"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 88840.0,
      "end_time": 90520.0,
      "text": "birds represent freedom."
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 91160.0,
      "end_time": 94655.0,
      "text": "This feather has enabled birds to conquer gravity"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 94680.0,
      "end_time": 97736.0,
      "text": "and take to the air in an extraordinary way."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 97760.0,
      "end_time": 100840.0,
      "text": "Don&#39;t you sometimes wish you could fly like a bird?"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 102720.0,
      "end_time": 105295.0,
      "text": "Birds are my passion,"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 105320.0,
      "end_time": 109696.0,
      "text": "and I want to change the way each one of you thinks about them."
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 109720.0,
      "end_time": 113280.0,
      "text": "The easiest reason I love them so much is because they are beautiful."
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 114320.0,
      "end_time": 117616.0,
      "text": "There are 10,000 species in the world,"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 117640.0,
      "end_time": 121000.0,
      "text": "and each one of them is uniquely beautiful."
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 122480.0,
      "end_time": 123680.0,
      "text": "Birds are amazing,"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 124480.0,
      "end_time": 128176.0,
      "text": "and this talk is dedicated to all the birds of the world."
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 128199.00000000001,
      "end_time": 129775.00000000001,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 129800.00000000001,
      "end_time": 133536.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 133560.0,
      "end_time": 138960.0,
      "text": "Indeed, these birds have been part of our lives and cultures"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 138120.0,
      "end_time": 140776.0,
      "text": "all over the world for centuries,"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 140800.0,
      "end_time": 143936.0,
      "text": "and every society has a story about birds."
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 143960.0,
      "end_time": 147656.0,
      "text": "You probably have heard childhood stories of different birds"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 147680.0,
      "end_time": 149656.0,
      "text": "and how they relate with man."
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 149680.0,
      "end_time": 151496.0,
      "text": "I personally recently learned"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 151520.0,
      "end_time": 155296.0,
      "text": "that our human ancestors would follow flocks of vultures"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 155320.0,
      "end_time": 156736.0,
      "text": "and then they would help them"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 156760.0,
      "end_time": 160215.0,
      "text": "to identify where carcasses have been dropped by large carnivores,"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 160240.0,
      "end_time": 163600.0,
      "text": "and these humans will scavenge and eat part of that meat."
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 165960.0,
      "end_time": 169456.0,
      "text": "Birds have been used as brands and labels all over the world."
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 169480.0,
      "end_time": 170816.0,
      "text": "You know the bald eagle?"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 170840.0,
      "end_time": 173616.0,
      "text": "It was chosen as the national emblem for the US"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 173640.0,
      "end_time": 175775.0,
      "text": "because of its majestic strength,"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 175800.0,
      "end_time": 177160.0,
      "text": "beautiful looks"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 177400.0,
      "end_time": 178560.0,
      "text": "and even a long lifespan."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 179520.0,
      "end_time": 181560.0,
      "text": "And just like us humans"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 181800.0,
      "end_time": 185616.0,
      "text": "who have managed to live in virtually all habitats of this earth,"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 185640.0,
      "end_time": 189550.0,
      "text": "birds have also conquered the world."
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 189800.0,
      "end_time": 192160.0,
      "text": "From birds such as these beautiful penguins"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 192400.0,
      "end_time": 194456.0,
      "text": "that live in the cold ice caps"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 194480.0,
      "end_time": 196536.0,
      "text": "to even others like the larks,"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 196560.0,
      "end_time": 199696.0,
      "text": "who live in the hottest deserts you can imagine."
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 199720.0,
      "end_time": 202240.0,
      "text": "Indeed, these species have conquered this world."
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 203320.0,
      "end_time": 205976.0,
      "text": "Birds also build houses like us."
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 206000.0,
      "end_time": 208960.0,
      "text": "The real pros in housebuilding"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 208120.0,
      "end_time": 210240.0,
      "text": "are a group of birds we call the weaverbirds,"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 211400.0,
      "end_time": 212456.0,
      "text": "and this name they were given"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 212480.0,
      "end_time": 215000.0,
      "text": "because of the way in which they weave their nests."
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 215720.0,
      "end_time": 217296.0,
      "text": "An interesting one:"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 217320.0,
      "end_time": 220696.0,
      "text": "birds also love and date just like us humans."
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 220720.0,
      "end_time": 226576.0,
      "text": "In fact, you&#39;ll be surprised to know that males dress to impress the women,"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 226600.0,
      "end_time": 228176.0,
      "text": "and I&#39;ll show you how."
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 228200.0,
      "end_time": 230736.0,
      "text": "So here we have a long-tailed widowbird,"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 230760.0,
      "end_time": 233160.0,
      "text": "and this is how they would normally look."
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 233400.0,
      "end_time": 235456.0,
      "text": "But when it comes to the breeding season,"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 235480.0,
      "end_time": 237775.0,
      "text": "everything changes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 237800.0,
      "end_time": 239776.0,
      "text": "and this is how he looks."
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 239800.0,
      "end_time": 241960.0,
      "text": "(Audience murmurs)"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 241120.0,
      "end_time": 242360.0,
      "text": "Yeah?"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 243320.0,
      "end_time": 246976.0,
      "text": "Birds also, multiple species of them,"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 247000.0,
      "end_time": 250576.0,
      "text": "do love to touch and cuddle just like humans."
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 250600.0,
      "end_time": 252896.0,
      "text": "And I know you&#39;re wondering about this one."
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 252920.0,
      "end_time": 255335.0,
      "text": "Yes, they kiss too,"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 255360.0,
      "end_time": 257560.0,
      "text": "sometimes very deeply."
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 257790.00000000003,
      "end_time": 260296.00000000003,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 260320.0,
      "end_time": 262896.0,
      "text": "Some have even learned to cheat on their spouses."
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 262920.0,
      "end_time": 263936.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 263960.0,
      "end_time": 265936.0,
      "text": "For example, the African jacana:"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 265960.0,
      "end_time": 268375.0,
      "text": "the females will mate with multiple males"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 268399.0,
      "end_time": 271336.0,
      "text": "and then she takes off to find other males to mate with"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 271360.0,
      "end_time": 274536.0,
      "text": "and she leaves the male behind to take care of the chicks."
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 274560.0,
      "end_time": 276176.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 276200.0,
      "end_time": 279360.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 280120.0,
      "end_time": 282336.0,
      "text": "And birds help us so much,"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 282360.0,
      "end_time": 286616.0,
      "text": "and they play very crucial roles in our ecosystems each day."
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 286640.0,
      "end_time": 288895.0,
      "text": "Vultures clean up our environment"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 288920.0,
      "end_time": 292296.0,
      "text": "by literally digesting disease-causing pathogens,"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 292320.0,
      "end_time": 296176.0,
      "text": "and they finish carcasses that would otherwise cost us lots of money"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 296200.0,
      "end_time": 298960.0,
      "text": "to clear from the environment."
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 298120.0,
      "end_time": 302560.0,
      "text": "A sizable flock of vultures is capable of bringing down a carcass"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 302800.0,
      "end_time": 304376.0,
      "text": "the size of a zebra straight to the bone"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 304400.0,
      "end_time": 306320.0,
      "text": "within just about 30 minutes."
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 307240.0,
      "end_time": 310856.0,
      "text": "Owls help to rid the environments of rodents"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 310880.0,
      "end_time": 313695.0,
      "text": "and this helps us a lot because it saves us money --"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 313720.0,
      "end_time": 315960.0,
      "text": "we don&#39;t lose our crops --"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 315120.0,
      "end_time": 318160.0,
      "text": "and secondly, we don&#39;t have to buy harmful chemicals"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 318400.0,
      "end_time": 319800.0,
      "text": "to handle these rodents."
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 321280.0,
      "end_time": 324496.0,
      "text": "The beautiful sunbirds we see in our environments"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 324520.0,
      "end_time": 326936.0,
      "text": "are part of nature&#39;s pollination crew,"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 326960.0,
      "end_time": 330296.0,
      "text": "and they help our plants to form fruits."
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 330320.0,
      "end_time": 332896.0,
      "text": "Together with other pollinators like insects,"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 332920.0,
      "end_time": 334456.0,
      "text": "they have actually helped us"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 334480.0,
      "end_time": 338320.0,
      "text": "to get most of the food crops that we depend on for many years."
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 339920.0,
      "end_time": 344496.0,
      "text": "Unfortunately, the story of birds is by far not perfect."
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 344520.0,
      "end_time": 349135.0,
      "text": "They are faced by numerous challenges every day wherever they live."
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 349160.0,
      "end_time": 350856.0,
      "text": "Top on the threats facing birds"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 350880.0,
      "end_time": 352336.0,
      "text": "is habitat loss"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 352360.0,
      "end_time": 354760.0,
      "text": "and reduced food availability."
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 355440.0,
      "end_time": 358936.0,
      "text": "Birds are also hunted, especially migratory species"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 358960.0,
      "end_time": 361479.0,
      "text": "and ducks that congregate in water bodies."
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 362640.0,
      "end_time": 366296.0,
      "text": "Poisoning is happening to flocks that like to stick together,"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 366320.0,
      "end_time": 368520.0,
      "text": "especially in places like rice schemes."
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 369720.0,
      "end_time": 373136.0,
      "text": "Moreover, power lines are electrocuting birds"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 373160.0,
      "end_time": 375536.0,
      "text": "and wind farms are slicing birds"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 375560.0,
      "end_time": 377480.0,
      "text": "when they fly through the blades."
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 378320.0,
      "end_time": 381336.0,
      "text": "Recently, we&#39;ve heard the talk of climate change"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 381360.0,
      "end_time": 383176.0,
      "text": "making a lot of headlines,"
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 383200.0,
      "end_time": 385216.0,
      "text": "and it&#39;s also affecting birds,"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 385240.0,
      "end_time": 389616.0,
      "text": "because birds are being forced to migrate to better breeding and feeding grounds"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 389640.0,
      "end_time": 391776.0,
      "text": "because unfortunately where they used to live"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 391800.0,
      "end_time": 393000.0,
      "text": "is no longer habitable."
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 394160.0,
      "end_time": 396496.0,
      "text": "My own perspective towards birds was changed"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 396520.0,
      "end_time": 398695.0,
      "text": "when I was a small boy in high school,"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 398720.0,
      "end_time": 400376.0,
      "text": "and there was this boy who struck,"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 400400.0,
      "end_time": 403799.0,
      "text": "injuring the wing and the leg of a bird we called the augur buzzard."
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 404480.0,
      "end_time": 406376.0,
      "text": "I was standing there,"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 406400.0,
      "end_time": 408335.0,
      "text": "just a mere 14-year-old,"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 408360.0,
      "end_time": 411896.0,
      "text": "and I imagined a human being in a similar situation,"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 411920.0,
      "end_time": 413960.0,
      "text": "because this bird could not help itself."
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 414480.0,
      "end_time": 418216.0,
      "text": "So even if I was hardly any biologist by then,"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 418240.0,
      "end_time": 422136.0,
      "text": "I gathered with three of my friends and we decided to house the bird"
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 422160.0,
      "end_time": 424880.0,
      "text": "until it had regained strength and then let it free."
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 425680.0,
      "end_time": 430160.0,
      "text": "Interestingly, it accepted to feed on beef from our school kitchen,"
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 430400.0,
      "end_time": 434136.0,
      "text": "and we hunted termites around the compound for its dinner every day."
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 434160.0,
      "end_time": 436376.0,
      "text": "After a few days, it had regained strength"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 436400.0,
      "end_time": 437655.0,
      "text": "and we released it."
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 437680.0,
      "end_time": 440216.0,
      "text": "We were so happy to see it flap its wings"
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 440240.0,
      "end_time": 442136.0,
      "text": "and fly off gracefully."
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 442160.0,
      "end_time": 445600.0,
      "text": "And that experience changed the way we looked at birds."
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 446640.0,
      "end_time": 449616.0,
      "text": "We went on to actually make a magazine,"
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 449640.0,
      "end_time": 451856.0,
      "text": "and we called it the Hawk Magazine,"
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 451880.0,
      "end_time": 453976.0,
      "text": "and this was in honor of this bird"
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 454000.0,
      "end_time": 457936.0,
      "text": "that we had helped within our own high school."
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 457960.0,
      "end_time": 462239.0,
      "text": "Those experiences in high school made me the conservationist I am today."
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 463400.0,
      "end_time": 466776.0,
      "text": "And a passion for birds should especially matter for Africa"
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 466800.0,
      "end_time": 468256.0,
      "text": "and all Africans,"
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 468280.0,
      "end_time": 470575.0,
      "text": "because among all other continents,"
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 470600.0,
      "end_time": 473536.0,
      "text": "Africa hosts some of the most amazing bird species"
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 473560.0,
      "end_time": 475816.0,
      "text": "you can find anywhere in the world."
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 475840.0,
      "end_time": 478655.0,
      "text": "Imagine having a name like \"shoebill.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 478680.0,
      "end_time": 480656.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s the name of that bird."
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 480680.0,
      "end_time": 484256.0,
      "text": "And there are countries like DR Congo,"
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 484280.0,
      "end_time": 486816.0,
      "text": "Tanzania, Uganda and Kenya"
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 486840.0,
      "end_time": 490376.0,
      "text": "who are leading the continent in highest numbers of diversity"
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 490400.0,
      "end_time": 491780.0,
      "text": "when it comes to the species."
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 493400.0,
      "end_time": 495496.0,
      "text": "These birds continue to provide the continent"
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 495520.0,
      "end_time": 499976.0,
      "text": "with very crucial ecosystem services that Africa needs."
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 500000.0,
      "end_time": 502856.0,
      "text": "Moreover, there is huge potential"
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 502880.0,
      "end_time": 506280.0,
      "text": "for Africa to lead the world in avian tourism."
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 507480.0,
      "end_time": 510176.0,
      "text": "The economy will definitely benefit."
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 510200.0,
      "end_time": 514415.0,
      "text": "Imagine how many communities will benefit from groups of tourists"
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 514440.00000000006,
      "end_time": 517616.00000000006,
      "text": "visiting their villages just to see the endemic birds"
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 517640.0,
      "end_time": 520390.0,
      "text": "that can only be found in those villages."
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 521320.00000000006,
      "end_time": 523400.00000000006,
      "text": "How can we help birds together?"
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 523799.0,
      "end_time": 526935.0,
      "text": "There is now a chance for all of you"
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 526960.0,
      "end_time": 528775.0,
      "text": "to turn your passion for birds"
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 528799.0,
      "end_time": 531696.0,
      "text": "into contributing to their continued survival,"
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 531720.0,
      "end_time": 535559.0,
      "text": "and you can do that by becoming a citizen scientist."
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 536520.0,
      "end_time": 540216.0,
      "text": "Citizen science is a growing trend around the world,"
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 540240.0,
      "end_time": 543296.0,
      "text": "and we are having scenarios where people are sharing information"
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 543320.0,
      "end_time": 546296.0,
      "text": "with the rest of the community about traffic updates,"
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 546320.0,
      "end_time": 548576.0,
      "text": "security alerts and so on."
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 548600.0,
      "end_time": 552376.0,
      "text": "That is exactly what we realized as bird-watchers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 552400.0,
      "end_time": 555456.0,
      "text": "and we thought, because birds are found everywhere,"
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 555480.0,
      "end_time": 558656.0,
      "text": "if we&#39;ve got all of you and everyone else in Africa"
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 558680.0,
      "end_time": 561550.0,
      "text": "to tell us the birds they find where they live,"
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 561800.0,
      "end_time": 563496.0,
      "text": "where they school, or even where they work,"
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 563520.0,
      "end_time": 568550.0,
      "text": "then we can be able to come up with a map of every single species,"
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 568800.0,
      "end_time": 570816.0,
      "text": "and from there scientists will be able"
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 570840.0,
      "end_time": 573896.0,
      "text": "to actually prioritize conservation efforts"
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 573920.0,
      "end_time": 576376.0,
      "text": "to those habitats that matter the most."
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 576400.0,
      "end_time": 578456.0,
      "text": "Take for example these two projects,"
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 578480.0,
      "end_time": 580256.0,
      "text": "the Africa Raptor DataBank,"
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 580280.0,
      "end_time": 584136.0,
      "text": "which is mapping all birds of prey in the continent of Africa,"
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 584160.0,
      "end_time": 585456.0,
      "text": "and the Kenya Bird Map,"
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 585480.0,
      "end_time": 590416.0,
      "text": "which is mapping about 1,100 species that occur in my country, Kenya."
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 590440.0,
      "end_time": 593416.0,
      "text": "These two projects now have online databases"
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 593440.0,
      "end_time": 595896.0,
      "text": "that are allowing people to submit data,"
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 595920.0,
      "end_time": 598896.0,
      "text": "and this is converted into very interactive websites"
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 598920.0,
      "end_time": 602000.0,
      "text": "that the public can consume and make decisions from."
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 602680.0,
      "end_time": 604935.0,
      "text": "But when we started, there was a big challenge."
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 604960.0,
      "end_time": 607416.0,
      "text": "We received many complaints from bird-watchers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 607440.0,
      "end_time": 608696.0,
      "text": "and they will say,"
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 608720.0,
      "end_time": 611560.0,
      "text": "\"I&#39;m in a village, and I cannot access a computer."
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 611800.0,
      "end_time": 613696.0,
      "text": "How do I tell you what birds live in my home,"
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 613720.0,
      "end_time": 616960.0,
      "text": "or where I school, or where I work?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 616120.0,
      "end_time": 621816.0,
      "text": "So we were forced to renovate our strategy and come up with a sustainable solution."
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 621840.0,
      "end_time": 623136.0,
      "text": "It was easy:"
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 623160.0,
      "end_time": 625376.0,
      "text": "we immediately realized that mobile phones"
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 625400.0,
      "end_time": 628550.0,
      "text": "were becoming increasingly common in Africa"
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 628800.0,
      "end_time": 630760.0,
      "text": "and most of the regions could get access to one."
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 631520.0,
      "end_time": 635216.0,
      "text": "So we came up with mobile phone applications"
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 635240.0,
      "end_time": 638376.0,
      "text": "that you can use on your iPhone and on your Android phone,"
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 638400.0,
      "end_time": 640496.0,
      "text": "and we made them freely available"
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 640520.0,
      "end_time": 644776.0,
      "text": "for every bird-watching enthusiast out there."
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 644800.0,
      "end_time": 649550.0,
      "text": "So we came up with BirdLasser, which is used by the Kenya Bird Map,"
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 649800.0,
      "end_time": 652776.0,
      "text": "and also we have the African Raptor Observations,"
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 652800.0,
      "end_time": 655856.0,
      "text": "which is now used by the African Raptor DataBank."
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 655880.0,
      "end_time": 658160.0,
      "text": "This was a huge breakthrough in our work"
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 658400.0,
      "end_time": 660736.0,
      "text": "and it made us get enormous amounts of data"
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 660760.0,
      "end_time": 663560.0,
      "text": "from every birder out there in the regions."
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 664400.0,
      "end_time": 666776.0,
      "text": "With this, we realized that citizen science"
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 666800.0,
      "end_time": 668856.0,
      "text": "is indeed very powerful,"
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 668880.0,
      "end_time": 671920.0,
      "text": "the reason being, citizen science is adaptive."
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 672920.0,
      "end_time": 676376.0,
      "text": "And we were able to actually convert many bird-watchers"
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 676400.0,
      "end_time": 678920.0,
      "text": "to start sharing new information with us."
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 682240.0,
      "end_time": 683456.0,
      "text": "When we were starting,"
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 683480.0,
      "end_time": 686560.0,
      "text": "we didn&#39;t know that birds could be a huge gateway"
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 686800.0,
      "end_time": 688880.0,
      "text": "to approaching conservation of other forms of animals."
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 689600.0,
      "end_time": 692856.0,
      "text": "Interestingly, now in the Virtual Museum for Africa,"
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 692880.0,
      "end_time": 696560.0,
      "text": "we have maps for dragonflies and damselflies,"
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 696800.0,
      "end_time": 697816.0,
      "text": "butterflies and moths,"
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 697840.0,
      "end_time": 701976.0,
      "text": "reptiles, frogs, orchids, spiders,"
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 702000.0,
      "end_time": 705856.0,
      "text": "scorpions, and yes, we are even mapping mushrooms."
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 705880.0,
      "end_time": 708536.0,
      "text": "Who could have imagined mapping mushrooms?"
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 708560.0,
      "end_time": 713136.0,
      "text": "So this showed us that indeed we&#39;ve created a community of people"
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 713160.0,
      "end_time": 715520.0,
      "text": "who care about nature in Africa."
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 716720.0,
      "end_time": 718936.0,
      "text": "I hereby call upon all of you"
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 718960.0,
      "end_time": 722176.0,
      "text": "to join me in promoting the value of birds"
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 722200.0,
      "end_time": 723976.0,
      "text": "within your communities."
    },
    {
      "index": 239,
      "start_time": 724000.0,
      "end_time": 726656.0,
      "text": "Please just tell your friends about birds,"
    },
    {
      "index": 240,
      "start_time": 726680.0,
      "end_time": 730959.0,
      "text": "for we are always inclined to love and care for that which we know."
    },
    {
      "index": 241,
      "start_time": 731720.0,
      "end_time": 733976.0,
      "text": "Please spend a few minutes in your free time"
    },
    {
      "index": 242,
      "start_time": 734000.0,
      "end_time": 737960.0,
      "text": "when you are at work, at school, or maybe at home,"
    },
    {
      "index": 243,
      "start_time": 737120.0,
      "end_time": 740696.0,
      "text": "to at least look around you and see which beautiful birds are there."
    },
    {
      "index": 244,
      "start_time": 740720.0,
      "end_time": 742816.0,
      "text": "Come join us in citizen science"
    },
    {
      "index": 245,
      "start_time": 742840.0,
      "end_time": 746816.0,
      "text": "and tell us the birds you&#39;re finding in the places where you visit."
    },
    {
      "index": 246,
      "start_time": 746840.0,
      "end_time": 748136.0,
      "text": "Even simpler,"
    },
    {
      "index": 247,
      "start_time": 748160.0,
      "end_time": 750776.0,
      "text": "you could buy your child or your sibling"
    },
    {
      "index": 248,
      "start_time": 750800.0,
      "end_time": 752616.0,
      "text": "a pair of binoculars"
    },
    {
      "index": 249,
      "start_time": 752640.0,
      "end_time": 753976.0,
      "text": "or a bird book"
    },
    {
      "index": 250,
      "start_time": 754000.0,
      "end_time": 757496.0,
      "text": "and let them just appreciate how beautiful these birds are."
    },
    {
      "index": 251,
      "start_time": 757520.0,
      "end_time": 760376.0,
      "text": "Because maybe one day they will want to care"
    },
    {
      "index": 252,
      "start_time": 760400.0,
      "end_time": 763295.0,
      "text": "for that one which they know and love."
    },
    {
      "index": 253,
      "start_time": 763320.0,
      "end_time": 766960.0,
      "text": "The children indeed are our future."
    },
    {
      "index": 254,
      "start_time": 766120.0,
      "end_time": 769616.0,
      "text": "Let us please teach them to love our feathermakers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 255,
      "start_time": 769640.0,
      "end_time": 771576.0,
      "text": "because the love of birds"
    },
    {
      "index": 256,
      "start_time": 771600.0,
      "end_time": 775936.0,
      "text": "can be a huge gateway to appreciating all forms of nature."
    },
    {
      "index": 257,
      "start_time": 775960.0,
      "end_time": 777176.0,
      "text": "Thank you very much."
    },
    {
      "index": 258,
      "start_time": 777200.0,
      "end_time": 782456.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 259,
      "start_time": 782480.0,
      "end_time": 783920.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    }
  ]
}